title: Hour 2 - Kevin Durant's Shock Is Laughable, Mike Tannenbaum
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Kevin Durant's Shock Is Laughable, Mike Tannenbaum
description:
Dan thinks Brooklyn Nets superstar Kevin Durant expressing shock over the firing of HC Steve Nash is disingenuous. And he talks to NFL insider Mike Tannenbaum about the moves that did and didn't happen at the NFL trade deadline.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
